  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Core Rules and Setup\n\r\n- The objective is to build four stacks (one
    for each suit) in ascending order from Ace to King.\r\n- Tableau Building: In
    the main play area, cards must be placed in descending order and alternating
    colors (e.g., a red 7 can only be placed on a black 8).\r\n- Empty Spaces: Only
    a King (K)\u2014or a sequence starting with a King\u2014can be moved into an
    empty column on the tableau.\r\n- Stock Pile: When you run out of moves, you
    draw cards from the remaining deck.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nQuick
    Winning Strategies\n\r\n- Expose Hidden Cards: Prioritize moves that flip over
    face-down cards on the tableau.\r\n- Move Aces Immediately: Always move Aces
    and 2s to the foundation piles as soon as they appear.\r\n- Manage Empty Slots:
    Don't empty a column unless you have a King ready to fill it; an empty spot is
    useless without a King."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a026544f366ba7e4d87cdea1457d5ee9, type: 2}
